name: Back to School - Princess Anna Dress up Game
name_original: Back to School - Princess Anna Dress up Game
description:
Princess Anna is going back to school, she is excited because she is going back to meet her friends.
It's Monday and the time is fast, you have to choose some suits for school. Your closet is so large that it is difficult to choose, we have to help it !.

Let's dress Anna in a beautiful uniform. She goes to the salon to get her elegant hairstyle; Also choose some heels, and many other accessories, that every girl should use. She will be the center of attention at school.

There is a great variety of suits to combine as you like.

Do you want to be a fashion designer?
Use your creativity to put together the best combinations.

Be a fashion designer and have fun with our dress up games for girls.

Dress up games for girls.
